---
// Equipment section component
---

<section id="sprzet" class="section equipment-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="equipment-content">
      <div class="equipment-image-container">
        <img
          src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1420744/pexels-photo-1420744.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1"
          alt="Koparka - profesjonalny sprzęt budowlany"
          class="equipment-image"
        />
        <div class="equipment-image-accent"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="equipment-text">
        <h2 class="equipment-title">Nasz sprzęt – gwarancja solidnej pracy</h2>

        <p class="equipment-description">
          Dysponujemy nowoczesnym parkiem maszynowym, który pozwala nam realizować nawet najbardziej wymagające projekty. Nasze koparki, ładowarki i wywrotki zapewniają precyzję i efektywność na każdym etapie prac ziemnych. Dzięki temu możemy zagwarantować sprawną realizację wykopów, niwelacji terenu oraz transportu materiałów sypkich.
        </p>

        <div class="equipment-benefits">
          <h3 class="benefits-title">Profesjonalny sprzęt to:</h3>

          <ul class="benefits-list">
            <li class="benefit-item">
              <span class="check-icon">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
                </svg>
              </span>
              <span>Szybsza i dokładniejsza realizacja zleceń</span>
            </li>

            <li class="benefit-item">
              <span class="check-icon">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
                </svg>
              </span>
              <span>Możliwość pracy w każdych warunkach terenowych</span>
            </li>

            <li class="benefit-item">
              <span class="check-icon">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
                </svg>
              </span>
              <span>Maksymalne bezpieczeństwo i precyzja</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="equipment-cta">
          <p class="cta-text">Zaufaj specjalistom z doświadczeniem i zapleczem technicznym na najwyższym poziomie!</p>
          <a href="#kontakt" class="cta-button primary">
            <span>Skontaktuj się z nami</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .equipment-section {
    background-color: #f5f5f5;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 5rem 0
  }

  .container {
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .equipment-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .equipment-image-container {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    height: 400px;
  }

  .equipment-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.5s ease;
  }

  .equipment-image-container:hover .equipment-image {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .equipment-image-accent {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 5px;
    background-color: #ffc107;
  }

  .equipment-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .equipment-title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #111111;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .equipment-title::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 80px;
    height: 3px;
    background-color: #ffc107;
  }

  .equipment-description {
    color: #555555;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .equipment-benefits {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .benefits-title {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #333333;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .benefits-list {
    list-style: none;
  }

  .benefit-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .check-icon {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    color: #ffc107;
    margin-right: 1rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .equipment-cta {
    background-color: rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.1);
    border-left: 3px solid #ffc107;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
  }

  .cta-text {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #333333;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .cta-button.primary {
    background-color: #ffc107;
    color: #111111;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.3);
  }

  .cta-button.primary:hover {
    background-color: #ffd54f;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 25px rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.4);
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .equipment-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .equipment-image-container {
      height: 500px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .equipment-title {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }

    .equipment-image-container {
      height: 300px;
    }
  }
</style>

